PrecisAmendment (SCHEDULE No. 895) to the FOOD AND DRUG REGULATIONS which increases the maximum level of "calcium chloride" that may be used as a firming agent in a number of standardized and unstandardized foods, including pickles and relishes, from 0.1% to 0.4%.
